		"description": "<p>When you select this archetype at 3rd level, you gain proficiency with Stealth if you do not have it already.</p>\n<p>If you are already proficient with Stealth, you gain proficiency in another skill from the scholar list. You also gain an expertise die on Stealth checks. At level 7, this die increases to d6. At 10, it increases to d8 and your maximum size of an expertise die on Stealth checks increases to d10. At level 14, this die increases to a d10 and your maximum size of expertise die on Stealth checks is d12. You may always choose to use Intelligence on Stealth checks.</p>\n<p>In addition, you add @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-feats.Item.n8rh27w94jgwa4pm]{Combat Thievery} to your list of available bonus feats.</p>",
